items.title: Fulmer has season-ending elbow surgery
items.summary: Michael Fulmer's followup to his American League Rookie of the Year campaign is officially over. The All-Star right-hander underwent ulnar nerve transposition surgery in his right elbow to eliminate the numbness and tingling that had increasingly bothered him this season.
